{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this <strong>demo</strong>, players will be able to experience the <strong>full interactive tutorial</strong> that will teach the core mechanics of the game, as well as touch upon some strategic possibilities.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Furthermore, demo players will be able to try out <strong>playing the real online game</strong> with other players during scheduled events that can be <strong>found in our Discord.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>  </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456440/extras/Twitter_Banner.png?t=1737538022\" /><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Tutorial is divided into 3 chapters:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chapter 1</strong> teaches the basic mechanics around movement, player UI, day/night cycles, different factions and roles, completing tasks, and how the voting round works.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chapter 2</strong> dives deeper into specific character abilities and teaches players how to use the many in-game mechanics to solve murders and find out who the killers are. Players will also learn about the Safe Zone and its features.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chapter 3</strong> gives players their first taste of what it's like to be the killer, and how they can still be a valuable asset to their team after being killed. It also shows the player how the unique Werewolf character is player.\u00a0<br>  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Conquer the Castle in Style!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456440/extras/CosmeticShowcase.gif?t=1737538022\" /><strong><br> <br>Complete Tasks as Protectors &amp; Expose the Satanic Among You!</stro